data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the beautiful community of Mallard View.  This traditional  5-bedroom, 3-bathroom home boasts a primary suite on the main level, an open concept design, two separate living spaces with fireplaces, and an outdoor oasis complete with a pool and expansive outdoor living area. Upon entering, you'll be greeted by a open foyer that leads to the spacious and light-filled main living area. The living room features soaring ceilings, a cozy fireplace, and large windows that offer panoramic views of the backyard. The gourmet kitchen is a chef's delight, equipped with high-end stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, and a center island. This is a stunning property that is waiting for you.
